13, \"text\": \"Judo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The refreshment options were wide.\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3205, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The refreshment options\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3194}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We had burritos, crepes, Peruvian sausage and burgers to choose from - and none were far above the prohibitive prices that Parisian nourishment tends to be (ham and cheese on toast, with a fancy name, commands a hefty tariff of up to 16 euros in the swanky centre).\", \"from\": 3206, \"to\": 3471, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3231, \"end\": 3239, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peruvian_cuisine\", \"score\": 0.9999972597617016, \"rank\": 2.7374729733598807e-06, \"text\": \"Peruvian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peruvian_cuisine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Peruvian_cuisine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"crepes\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3229}, {\"ngram\": \"burgers\", \"from\": 3252, \"to\": 3259}, {\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3285}, {\"ngram\": \"the prohibitive prices\", \"from\": 3301, \"to\": 3323}, {\"ngram\": \"Parisian nourishment\", \"from\": 3329, \"to\": 3349}, {\"ngram\": \"(ham\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3366}, {\"ngram\": \"cheese\", \"from\": 3371, \"to\": 3377}, {\"ngram\": \"toast\", \"from\": 3381, \"to\": 3386}, {\"ngram\": \"a fancy name\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3405}, {\"ngram\": \"a hefty tariff\", \"from\": 3416, \"to\": 3430}, {\"ngram\": \"up to 16 euros\", \"from\": 3434, \"to\": 3448}, {\"ngram\": \"the swanky centre\", \"from\": 3452, \"to\": 3469}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A decent burger and chips - think trendy \\\"smash\\\" sandwiches and gastropub French fries, rather than McDonald's - was 14 euros.\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3599, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3547, \"end\": 3559, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_fries\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French fries\", \"types\": [\"Q2095\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_fries\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_fries\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A decent burger\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3488}, {\"ngram\": \"chips\", \"from\": 3493, \"to\": 3498}, {\"ngram\": \"trendy \\\"smash\\\" sandwiches\", \"from\": 3507, \"to\": 3532}, {\"ngram\": \"McDonald\", \"from\": 3573, \"to\": 3581}, {\"ngram\": \"14 euros\", \"from\": 3590, \"to\": 3598}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There was also an enticing vegan option, complete with a French touch.\", \"from\": 3600, \"to\": 3670, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3657, \"end\": 3669, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_house\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French touch\", \"types\": [\"Q188451\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_house\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_house\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an enticing vegan option\", \"from\": 3615, \"to\": 3639}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The burger van had an option curated by none other than Alain Ducasse, at a euro less than the beef choice.\", \"from\": 3671, \"to\": 3778, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3675, \"end\": 3685, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_truck\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"burger van\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_truck\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Food_truck\"}, {\"begin\": 3727, \"end\": 3740, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alain_Ducasse\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.819738683249234e-26, \"text\": \"Alain Ducasse\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alain_Ducasse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alain_Ducasse\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an option\", \"from\": 3690, \"to\": 3699}, {\"ngram\": \"none\", \"from\": 3711, \"to\": 3715}, {\"ngram\": \"the beef choice\", \"from\": 3762, \"to\": 3777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sadly it had sold out - which is probably a good sign.\", \"from\": 3779, \"to\": 3833, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a good sign\", \"from\": 3821, \"to\": 3832}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In contrast, IOC-approved venue kiosks at the Stade de France offered spartan, tired looking sandwiches at 8.50 euros each, mystery-meat hot dogs for 9.50 or an \\\"egg muffin\\\" (one of only two vegetarian options) at eight euros.\", \"from\": 3835, \"to\": 4061, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3881, \"end\": 3896, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Stade de France\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stade_de_France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"contrast\", \"from\": 3838, \"to\": 3846}, {\"ngram\": \"IOC-approved venue kiosks\", \"from\": 3848, \"to\": 3873}, {\"ngram\": \"spartan, tired looking sandwiches\", \"from\": 3905, \"to\": 3938}, {\"ngram\": \"8.50 euros\", \"from\": 3942, \"to\": 3952}, {\"ngram\": \"each, mystery-meat hot dogs\", \"from\": 3953, \"to\": 3980}, {\"ngram\": \"an \\\"egg muffin\", \"from\": 3993, \"to\": 4007}, {\"ngram\": \"only two vegetarian options\", \"from\": 4017, \"to\": 4044}, {\"ngram\": \"eight euros\", \"from\": 4049, \"to\": 4060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some places had a slice of stodgy looking quiche at the same price.\", \"from\": 4062, \"to\": 4129, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some places\", \"from\": 4062, \"to\": 4073}, {\"ngram\": \"a slice\", \"from\": 4078, \"to\": 4085}, {\"ngram\": \"stodgy looking quiche\", \"from\": 4089, \"to\": 4110}, {\"ngram\": \"the same price\", \"from\": 4114, \"to\": 4128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The only thing vegans can eat at venues is fries.\", \"from\": 4130, \"to\": 4179, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The only thing vegans\", \"from\": 4130, \"to\": 4151}, {\"ngram\": \"venues\", \"from\": 4163, \"to\": 4169}, {\"ngram\": \"fries\", \"from\": 4173, \"to\": 4178}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Drinks included champagne, of course, (12 euros a glass or 70 a bottle) and beer, which was served in 480ml cups at seven euros a pop.\", \"from\": 4181, \"to\": 4315, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Drinks\", \"from\": 4181, \"to\": 4187}, {\"ngram\": \"champagne\", \"from\": 4197, \"to\": 4206}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 4211, \"to\": 4217}, {\"ngram\": \"12 euros\", \"from\": 4220, \"to\": 4228}, {\"ngram\": \"a bottle\", \"from\": 4243, \"to\": 4251}, {\"ngram\": \"beer\", \"from\": 4257, \"to\": 4261}, {\"ngram\": \"480ml cups\", \"from\": 4283, \"to\": 4293}, {\"ngram\": \"seven euros\", \"from\": 4297, \"to\": 4308}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Again, not far above the prices in bars outside the Olympic bubble.\", \"from\": 4317, \"to\": 4384, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the prices\", \"from\": 4338, \"to\": 4348}, {\"ngram\": \"bars\", \"from\": 4352, \"to\": 4356}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic bubble\", \"from\": 4365, \"to\": 4383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bartender confirmed that champagne sales had been steady.\", \"from\": 4385, \"to\": 4446, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bartender\", \"from\": 4385, \"to\": 4398}, {\"ngram\": \"champagne sales\", \"from\": 4414, \"to\": 4429}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And unlike the concessions inside venues, the beer and wine actually contained alcohol.\", \"from\": 4447, \"to\": 4534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the concessions\", \"from\": 4458, \"to\": 4473}, {\"ngram\": \"venues\", \"from\": 4481, \"to\": 4487}, {\"ngram\": \"the beer\", \"from\": 4489, \"to\": 4497}, {\"ngram\": \"wine\", \"from\": 4502, \"to\": 4506}, {\"ngram\": \"alcohol\", \"from\": 4526, \"to\": 4533}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In venues, the only choice apart from water and Coca-Cola brands is zero per cent Kronenbourg at eight euros for half a litre.\", \"from\": 4536, \"to\": 4662, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"venues\", \"from\": 4539, \"to\": 4545}, {\"ngram\": \"the only choice\", \"from\": 4547, \"to\": 4562}, {\"ngram\": \"water\", \"from\": 4574, \"to\": 4579}, {\"ngram\": \"Coca-Cola brands\", \"from\": 4584, \"to\": 4600}, {\"ngram\": \"cent\", \"from\": 4613, \"to\": 4617}, {\"ngram\": \"eight euros\", \"from\": 4633, \"to\": 4644}, {\"ngram\": \"half a litre\", \"from\": 4649, \"to\": 4661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Venues do, however, have free water stations for people to fill up bottles they bring.\", \"from\": 4663, \"to\": 4749, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Venues\", \"from\": 4663, \"to\": 4669}, {\"ngram\": \"free water stations\", \"from\": 4688, \"to\": 4707}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 4712, \"to\": 4718}, {\"ngram\": \"bottles\", \"from\": 4730, \"to\": 4737}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yes, alcohol is not the be-all-and-end-all at sporting events, but it would be nice for the IOC to treat their fans like adults - and cater to people's choices that go beyond overpriced, beige, wheat-based food options.\", \"from\": 4751, \"to\": 4970, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4843, \"end\": 4846, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0088671961598304e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"alcohol\", \"from\": 4756, \"to\": 4763}, {\"ngram\": \"-end\", \"from\": 4785, \"to\": 4789}, {\"ngram\": \"sporting events\", \"from\": 4797, \"to\": 4812}, {\"ngram\": \"their fans\", \"from\": 4856, \"to\": 4866}, {\"ngram\": \"adults\", \"from\": 4872, \"to\": 4878}, {\"ngram\": \"cater\", \"from\": 4885, \"to\": 4890}, {\"ngram\": \"people's choices\", \"from\": 4894, \"to\": 4910}, {\"ngram\": \"overpriced, beige, wheat-based food options\", \"from\": 4926, \"to\": 4969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Bravo Paris 2024 for providing this for the hoi polloi who do not have tickets, or who wish to relax in the sun before heading to the events they have paid handsomely for.\", \"from\": 4971, \"to\": 5142, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4971, \"end\": 4976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"score\": 0.9999943030737471, \"rank\": 4.905046349805176e-06, \"text\": \"Bravo\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\"}, {\"begin\": 4977, \"end\": 4987, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5804508528751807e-19, \"text\": \"Paris 2024\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/2024_Summer_Olympics\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the hoi polloi\", \"from\": 5011, \"to\": 5025}, {\"ngram\": \"tickets\", \"from\": 5042, \"to\": 5049}, {\"ngram\": \"the sun\", \"from\": 5075, \"to\": 5082}, {\"ngram\": \"the events\", \"from\": 5101, \"to\": 5111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the IOC, the message is \\\"doit faire mieux\\\" - must do better.\", \"from\": 5143, \"to\": 5207, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5151, \"end\": 5154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.0088671961598304e-19, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the message\", \"from\": 5156, \"to\": 5167}, {\"ngram\": \"doit faire mieux\", \"from\": 5172, \"to\": 5188}]}